result.name: Cali-Mex Bar & Grill

reviews.text:
Good for a quick bite to eat, great service and friendly staff. Value isn't bad but isn't the height of Mexican cuisine. 

Good for what it is
Awesome food but not too honest
Beer tap at your seat and several varieties of beans. If you're away from the u.s. for more than 6 months you can fool yourself into thinking it's decent tex-mex. Generous with the queso.

I like Cali-Mex and am glad that they have finally come to understand that main courses should be delivered at the same time. Now, fix that thing called a milkshake; a milkshake is glass filled with ice cream, topped off with milk and blended. It is not flavored milk and ice.

Lastly, smile while serving and taking orders or do something else for employment.
Amazing food! Best nachos I've ever had and I'm from Tucson AZ. Good vegan options for every thing. Come to Chengdu! We need good Mexican food here.
